For Windows Use Only

Step 1
Download Powertoys on Microsoft
once installed,search on your windows and open it

Step 2
Launch Host File Editor
Click on New Entry and Set Address to 127.0.0.1 and Hosts to car4sure.local
Set Address to ::1 and Hosts to car4sure.local
Now you have set your Server on your machine.

Step 3
Download Xampp and run installation
once installed go to this location "C:\xampp2\apache\conf\extra\httpd-vhosts.conf"
open httpd-vhosts.conf on your VSC or IDE
then paste this at the bottom of the code
"<VirtualHost *:80>
    ServerName car4sure.local
    DocumentRoot C:/xampp/htdocs/1_car4sure/public    
    <Directory C:/xampp/htdocs/1_car4sure/public>
        DirectoryIndex index.php
        AllowOverride All
        Require all granted
    </Directory>
 </VirtualHost>"
 NB please note '1_car4sure' folder can differ depending on where your root folder has been saved by make sure to save path as the root folder of your project.
 Step 4
 Run composer install or composer update on you Terminal/CLI make sure to use CMD instead of powershell
 Once done Car4sure app or Task Management App should run as intended.

